  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bb4\u0bc8, \u0baa\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bb5\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bae\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Rain, strong winds likely - Department of Meteorology",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Meteorology has said that rain will occur several times in the Upper, Sabaragamuwa and North-West provinces and Nuwara Eliya, Kandy, Galle and Matara districts.",
        "Uva, Eastern and North Central Provinces and Mullaitivu District will experience rain or thundershowers at many places during afternoon or night.",
        "Strong winds of 40-50 km per hour may occur in the southern province from time to time.",
        "The general public is advised to take adequate precautions during thunderstorms to minimize possible damage due to temporary strong winds and lightning strikes.",
        "Scattered showers will occur over coastal areas from Puttalam through Colombo and Galle to Matara.",
        "Wind will blow from South-West direction with wind speed of 30-40 kmph. The wind speed may increase to 50-60 kmph in coastal areas from Colombo through Galle to Ambantota.",
        "The offshore seas from Colombo through Galle to Ambantota will be rough from time to time. Other seas surrounding the country are temperate."
      ],
